

#### Hangman Game with Daily Word from Dictionary.com
This is a Python script that allows you to play a Hangman game using the daily word from Dictionary.com's Word of the Day. The script extracts the daily word, its pronunciation, and its definition from the website and presents it to the player for guessing.

## Features
Extracts the daily word, pronunciation, and definition from Dictionary.com.
Provides a Hangman game interface for guessing the daily word.
Offers hints and a timer to aid the player during the game.
Tracks correct and incorrect guesses and displays them to the player.

## Dependencies
requests
bs4 (Beautiful Soup)
string
os
time
multiprocessing
logging

## How to Use
Clone the repository to your local machine.
Make sure you have Python installed on your machine.
Install the required dependencies using pip install -r requirements.txt.
Run the script using python hangman_game.py.
Follow the prompts to play the Hangman game with the daily word.

